Create Non Graded in Queue / Submits per Day 19

Step 1: Create Non Graded in Queue

- Copy (Ctrl + C) and Paste (Ctrl + V) the Avg Non Graded Days

- Remove the target goals field

- Replace the Indicator field with Ungraded in Queue

- Select Format under General X position = 230, Y position = 347, Width = 289, Height = 160

- Title = Non Graded in Queue




Step 2: Create Submits per Day

- Copy (Ctrl + C) and Paste (Ctrl + V) the Non Graded in Queue

- Replace Indicator with Submissions per Day

- Select Format under General X position = 230, Y position = 552, Width = 289, Height = 160

- Title = Submits per Day






How to  create KPI  cards.
